			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">1) PPU_DATA has a one-byte delay for reads. So you have to set the address, read, and then the <em>next</em> read has the value you cared about.<br />2) PPU_ADDR will automatically increment after every read or write. So you'd have to re-set the address between when you read from memory and when you wrote to it.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

