						<div class="postbody">The best practice I'd guess is having an algorithm that transforms an entity X/Y coordinate into a specific tile in your data, especially if you want to reuse the concept between both the player and enemies/other AI controlled stuff. The issue with scrolling games is of course that you'll be working with 16 bit coordinates on at least one axis.</div>

